<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="243" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[332,1280,902,1775]" pageId="16" pageNumber="243">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[332,460,1687,1711]" pageId="16" pageNumber="243">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species is dedicated to Alexander Riedel (Karlsruhe, 
<collectingCountry box="[1114,1215,1687,1711]" name="Germany" pageId="16" pageNumber="243">Germany</collectingCountry>
) who significantly contributed to the knowledge of New Guinean beetles and collected most of the scaphidiines dealt in the present paper.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
